title: #92Noon at The Fair! Korzo/Leopold/Birk
description: Twins talk to start show No. 5 at The Fair! Korzo stops by to talk about his Sunday morning show and some sports talkers. Jordan Leopold joins PA and Nordo and shares information about brain injuries and more. Plus, Matt Birk makes his regular appearance and even co-hosts the show with Nordo after PA leaves for Buffalo!
